{"id": "1497278216233029773", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 19, "author_id": "141021087747145728", "author_name": "smile.__", "author_bot": false, "content": "Traphase is kind of like Hearthstone, it's basically \n\n> build a Team, the order matters \n> > Teams are comprised of \"unique roles\" and still following the 2 realm rule\n> pick Wheels, the order does not matter\n> pick Posses, the order does not matter\n\n> Strikes are no-cost (cannot be modified by stagnation / other increase effects), and you have 2 of them\n> There are no corresponding \"Defense\" cards \n\nAll associated cards get shuffled, play till one team is eliminated.", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T16:49:04.834000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-24T16:50:42.596000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["877773186136174653"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1497011158400503968", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
